Dilacio perambulacionis inter terras de Mondurno et Balheluy.

90 It is . . . fully accordit betwyx . . . Richart . . . abbot of Abirbrothoc . . and . . . Schir Patrik lorde the Glammes ’. . . that the brefe of perambulacioun of the landis of Montdurnoch and the landis of Balheluy pertenand to the said abbot and lord sal be . . . delayt vnto Monunday the tend day of May next . . . and that Monunday the saide bref to procede wythowtyn . . . langar delay . . . and this poyntment the said parteys promittys . . . to . . . kep withowtyn ony new summondis . . . othir be thaimself or thair lawful procuratouris . . . In witnes of the quhilk thyng the sele of the said lorde the Glammys is to put at the Glam· mys the secunde day of O&ober the yer of God a thousande four hundyr and fyfty.
